    },
    {
      "id": "1498524295318601759",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-28T03:20:33.239+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "The situation is that the open GF180MCU PDK only provides 5 V standard cell, IO, and SRAM IP.\nHowever, I have a license to use 3.3 V standard cell, IO, and SRAM IP from eMemory.\n\nMy understanding is that if the design passes the required DRC checks, it should still be possible to tape it out in Run 2. I will also take full responsibility for the use of the eMemory IP and ensure that it complies with its licensing terms.\n\nCould you please confirm if this understanding is correct? Also, would I need to provide any additional documentation (for example, confirmation from eMemory) before tape-out?\n\nIn addition, are there any technical concerns with the padframe or COB packaging if the design uses 3.3 V IPs instead of the 5 V IPs provided in the open PDK?",
      "author": {
        "id": "683216938255777809",
        "name": "daobaanhvn",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "daobaanhvn",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "2026-04_media/4b7f5d556d30def875f2fbeddfbce6b2-57D15.png"
      },
      "attachments": [],
      "embeds": [],
      "stickers": [],
      "reactions": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "inlineEmojis": []
    },
    {
      "id": "1498555706801000658",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-28T05:25:22.32+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "The bond pads need to have the same dimensions and be at exactly the same position as in the default pad frame.",
      "author": {
        "id": "596068704471482370",
        "name": "246tnt",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "tnt",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
        "avatarUrl": "2026-04_media/88d17af9d19ab43565b0c46751ef7d12-DFEE5.png"
      },
      "attachments": [],
